    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>One of the three ancient categories of learning, along with the seven liberal and the seven mechanical arts; included magic, divination, and thievery.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
